    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/99796bb5f8a6bce519c04c50a482a861.poster.avif?t=1724196129\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/99796bb5f8a6bce519c04c50a482a861.webm?t=1724196129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/99796bb5f8a6bce519c04c50a482a861.mp4?t=1724196129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这是一个极简和放松的体验，拥有独特而引人入胜的视觉效果。您将成为一名铁路线管理员，负责向岛民提供资源，这些岛民居住在一个远离大陆的岛屿群中。创建一条安全路径，将所有资源送到岛上的小城镇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/50637907282c4ce3f468e3371e482132.poster.avif?t=1724196129\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/50637907282c4ce3f468e3371e482132.webm?t=1724196129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/50637907282c4ce3f468e3371e482132.mp4?t=1724196129\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>50个岛屿。<br></li><li>4种环境变化。<br></li><li>令人满意和放松的音效。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/626d76481bbbe686def8c4d0a0ad96da.poster.avif?t=1724196129\" width=612 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/626d76481bbbe686def8c4d0a0ad96da.webm?t=1724196129\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1807930/extras/626d76481bbb